<HEADLINE> EU, US Urge Bosnians to Vote in Municipal Elections </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, September 10 (Xinhua) -- The European Union and the
United States today urged Bosnians to cast their votes in the
coming municipal elections in their country.
