to tackle the problems local manufacturers face due to
international competition.
</P>
<P>
He said grants were given out, imports subsidized and
industries assisted to upgrade their technology.
</P>
<P>
The government has also made efforts to promote industrial
exports and services abroad and organize specialized trade
exhibitions to attract regional markets, the minister said.
</P>
<P>
He urged local industrialists to take full advantage of
financial incentives provided by the state to upgrade the
quality of their products.
</P>
<P>
With regard to the tourist industry, the minister said
despite negative predictions for 1997, the official statistics
have shown an increase, particularly in the summer period.
</P>
