<HEADLINE> French TV to Put on Movie on Post-War German POWs </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, September 11 (Xinhua) -- A French television channel
will put a documentary Friday on the history of 1 million German
prisoners of war (POW) who were detained in French concentration
camps from 1945 to 1948, according to le Monde today.
