Switzerland's Laurent Dufaux finished second with Spaniard
Fernando Escartin third.
</P>
<P>
The three men ahead of Jalabert overnight -- Michaelson,
Italian Fabrizio Guidi and Eleuterio Anguita of Spain -- were all
in the main pack. 
