RMC.
</P>
<P>
Longo still holds the world record for the world cycling record,
covering 48.159 kilometer (30.55 miles) last October in Mexico City.
</P>
<P>
She won her 11th world title last year at Lugano, Switzerland in
taking the road race.
</P>
<P>
She also won the road race at the Olympics but came in second in
the time trial. 
