1992 in the Golden Bridge Development Zone of the Pudong New Area,
makes nearly 100 varieties of refrigerators, air conditioners,
washing machines, microwave ovens and rice cookers.
</P>
<P>
The company is now China's largest exporter of appliances for
home use.  
