<HEADLINE> Australian Dollar Plunges To Two-Year Low </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, September 11 (Xinhua) -- The Australian dollar fell
to its lowest level in more than two years today after shocking
data of employment caught the markets by surprise.
</P>
