with the previous month.
</P>
<P>
Economists are now predicting the Reserve Bank of Australia
(RBA) will "sit tight" for a while on interest rates.
</P>
<P>
The RBA cut official interest rates five times between July
last year and July this year, the official cash rate is sitting at
5.0 percent.
