<HEADLINE> 200,000 Bangladeshi Women, Children Trafficked to </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, September 11 (Xinhua) -- About 200,000 women and
children of Bangladesh have been trafficked to Middle East in the
past 20 years, The United News of Bangladesh (UNB) reported
today.
</P>
<P>
