<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 11 (Xinhua) -- A group of 135 Vietnamese,
including 131 illegal immigrants and four migrants, returned by
air to Hanoi, Vietnam today on the 111th flight under the Orderly
Repatriation Program (ORP).
